      "updated": 1740000000000,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "PARALLELIZATION RULES\n\nRun PARALLEL when:\n  - Different files\n  - Different domains\n  - No data dependencies\n\nRun SEQUENTIAL when:\n  - Same file modified\n  - Data dependency exists\n  - Design before impl\n\nFile Conflict Prevention:\n  - Explicit file assignment\n  - Component boundaries\n  - Split overlaps into phases",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "rules_box",
      "originalText": "PARALLELIZATION RULES\n\nRun PARALLEL when:\n  - Different files\n  - Different domains\n  - No data dependencies\n\nRun SEQUENTIAL when:\n  - Same file modified\n  - Data dependency exists\n  - Design before impl\n\nFile Conflict Prevention:\n  - Explicit file assignment\n  - Component boundaries\n  - Split overlaps into phases",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
